headline: Cboe Global Markets Inc (CBOE) Q2 2025 Earnings Call Highlights: Record Revenue and Strategic Shifts
summary: Cboe Global Markets Inc (CBOE) reports a 14% increase in net revenue, strategic business closures, and strong growth in derivatives and Data Vantage segments.
